{"tid":51299,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸婦遭撤銷台灣身分證 雞蛋砸洗戶政事務所","createTime":"2016-12-23T06:15:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T06:28:52.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e8115e27c71e6c6ea75a12b57ffe79a318d747af","tid":51299,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:15:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dSqRZgYrHVo \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdSqRZgYrHVo%20&d=wTNcWpiBTO2ik9uJSyl1EYscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=e1edab25\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dSqRZgYrHVo </a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2016/new/dec/22/images/bigPic/400_400/1925541_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2016%2Fnew%2Fdec%2F22%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F400_400%2F1925541_1.jpg&h=fd2f7ab5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n中國女爭不到台灣身分證，今天與友人前往屏東內埔戶政事務所砸雞蛋。（記者邱芷柔翻） <br />\n<br />\n〔記者邱芷柔／屏東報導〕 <br />\n<br />\n嫁來台灣11年已取得身分證的中國福建應姓女子，日前遭前夫向移民署「自首」假結婚，屏東地檢署因追溯期已過裁定不起訴，但移民署調查兩人虛偽結婚屬實，兩人婚約「自始無效」，應女因此遭撤銷台灣身分證，喪失台灣身分的應女，今天上午夥同6名中華婦女聯合會工作人員到內埔戶政事務所怒砸雞蛋，被警方當場依侮辱公署罪現行犯逮捕。 <br />\n<br />\n47歲的應女在民國89年與台灣賴姓男子登記結婚，結婚後取得台灣身分證，但兩人感情生變，100年12月辦理離婚後，去年賴男再到移民署自首兩人是假結婚，屏東地檢署因追訴期已過予以不起訴處分，但移民署調查兩人虛偽結婚屬實，所以由戶政撤銷兩人婚姻登記，應女對判決提出行政訴訟及「確認婚姻存在」民事訴訟後，日前最高法院判應女敗訴，引起應女與聯合會人員不滿，到戶政事務所上演脫序行為。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2016/new/dec/22/images/bigPic/400_400/1925541_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2016%2Fnew%2Fdec%2F22%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F400_400%2F1925541_2.jpg&h=73a07d56&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n嫁來台灣11年已取得身分證的中國福建應姓女子，經移民署調查虛偽結婚後，撤銷應女台灣身分證。（記者邱芷柔攝）"},{"pid":"87e99037d697fc49820c0080bf14536f422448a2","tid":51299,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:16:14.000Z","msg":"「上班10多年來第一次遇到有人砸雞蛋！」戶政事務所人員被應女一行人突如其來的砸雞蛋舉動嚇傻，內埔戶政事務所也表示，他們是根據移民署調查結果，不起訴處分中的「虛偽結婚」而撤銷其結婚資格，「他們應該是找錯對象申訴了！」 <br />\n<br />\n在屏東開美髮店的應女，被撤銷身分後除了不能留在台灣，也沒辦法在台灣工作，對於之前的勞健保、保險等也都無效，屏東縣好好婦女權益發展協會也指出，除了移民署執行強制遣返，也可能讓應女成為在逃人口。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2016/new/dec/22/images/bigPic/400_400/1925541_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2016%2Fnew%2Fdec%2F22%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F400_400%2F1925541_3.jpg&h=bf0a7dc8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n內埔鄉戶政事務所今天遭蛋襲，嚇壞所內職員。（記者邱芷柔攝） <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2016/new/dec/22/images/bigPic/400_400/1925541_4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2016%2Fnew%2Fdec%2F22%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F400_400%2F1925541_4.jpg&h=b5cf74d1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n現場留下蛋洗痕跡。（記者邱芷柔攝）"},{"pid":"d2670f460044aeda7bf238dfa34f936e825cc292","tid":51299,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那狗"},{"pid":"d80f27a49a39e022e2f10b5df307a63338c7724b","tid":51299,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:20:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那狗</blockquote><br />\n人妻咁快手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n滾回去支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1964a3e36e850410ec9e54e369e8080ceb4ed058","tid":51299,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:24:33.000Z","msg":"台灣班蝗剩係扔雞蛋<br />\n香港個班蝗係扔汽油彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20604b00853778f9be42b445cbc89f09bf7cbace","tid":51299,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:28:09.000Z","msg":"又話唔恨台灣身份證又話台灣落後"},{"pid":"7f07c523e51956e1b064d848a1b2bc288cfdd28a","tid":51299,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:28:52.000Z","msg":"浪費咗幾年時間得個吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.diyad.cn/pic_biz/2015-04-05/bmShzgS3Ql0ALXVJq8cS470Za2O5OEEfJR3ZmiabauU8J9t6h5t2sF60Zfeia00Gexk3zFqFw0slSzZg4EhnmpZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.diyad.cn%2Fpic_biz%2F2015-04-05%2FbmShzgS3Ql0ALXVJq8cS470Za2O5OEEfJR3ZmiabauU8J9t6h5t2sF60Zfeia00Gexk3zFqFw0slSzZg4EhnmpZQ.jpg&h=07a51393&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}